From: Kees Cook <keescook@chromium.org>
Date: Thu, 17 Nov 2022 15:43:26 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] panic: Expose "warn_count" to sysfs
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.1.8
Git-commit: 8b05aa26336113c4cea25f1c333ee8cd4fc212a6

commit 8b05aa26336113c4cea25f1c333ee8cd4fc212a6 upstream.

Since Warn count is now tracked and is a fairly interesting signal, add
the entry /sys/kernel/warn_count to expose it to userspace.

